title: Pics: Is this the model who finally tamed Leo DiCaprio? Seemingly they're engaged after 4 months
text:
Four months. If the rumours are to be believed, that is impressive on all counts. Somewhere, Jack Nicholson is crying and slamming his fist on a mahogany surface .
One of the world's most famous bachelors - who has been linked with models (he has a type) Kat Torres, Erin Heatherton, Blake Lively, Bar Refaeli, Naomi Campbell, and Gisele BÃ¼ndchen, as well as Rihanna - has reportedly popped the question at (model) Kelly Rohrbach after four months of dating. When you know you just know.
According to reports via Elle: "Leo asked Kelly, 25, to be his girl over an intimate Italian dinner in New York City..." A source speaking via the outlet said: "It wasn't planned. It just happened. They were enjoying a bottle of red wine and engrossed in conversation as usual... She shares his passion for tackling social issues like global warming and world poverty. They connect on an intellectual level, which is new for him. She's much more than a pretty face."
Anyway, all of you are DYING to see what she looks like, so here are just some of the shots of her doing stuff on her Instagram.
Congrats to the couple - may they have a long and happy life together!
